1976年，里根向现任总统[[杰拉尔德·福特|福特]]发起挑战，争取成为共和党总统候选人。里根很快得到了美国保守联盟等志同道合组织的支持，成为了保守派的候选人，而福特总统则被认为是一个更为温和的共和党人。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/history/presidents/gf38.html|title=Biography of Gerald R. Ford|access-date=2007-03-29|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610172811/http://georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/history/presidents/gf38.html|archive-date=2010-06-10|via=National Archives and Records Administration|work=whitehouse.gov}} Ford considered himself as "a moderate in domestic affairs, a conservative in fiscal affairs, and a dyed-in-the-wool internationalist in foreign affairs".</ref>虽然里根输掉了共和党提名，但他在[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]获得了307张海选票，在怀俄明州获得了388张海选票，甚至于11月的选举人团投票中在[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]]获得了一张失信选举人票，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.archives.gov/federal-register/electoral-college/scores.html#1976|title=Electoral College Box Scores 1789–1996|access-date=2007-04-30|publisher=U.S. National Archives and Records Admin.|archive-date=2012-02-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65JLmKWn0?url=http://www.archives.gov/federal-register/electoral-college/scores.html#1976|dead-url=no}}</ref>而福特在该州击败了民主党挑战者[[吉米·卡特|吉米·卡特]]，但是福特最终在大选中败给了卡特。
