== 1980年总统大选 ==
{{main|1980年美国总统选举}}
里根的对手是现任民主党总统吉米·卡特和独立候选人[[约翰·B·安德森|约翰·B·安德森]]。<ref name="ReaganElections"/><ref name=1980DLAUSE>{{cite web| title=1980 Presidential General Election Results| url=https://uselectionatlas.org/RESULTS/national.php?year=1980&off=0&elect=0&f=0| website=uselectionatlas.org| publisher=Dave Leip's Atlas of U.S. Elections| access-date=2019-04-11| archive-date=2021-03-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308074429/https://uselectionatlas.org/RESULTS/national.php?year=1980&f=0&off=0&elect=0| dead-url=no}}</ref>他的支持者称赞他进行了乐观的竞选活动。<ref name="strategy campaigning">{{cite book | title = The Strategy of Campaigning | author1 = Skinner, Kudelia | author2 = Mesquita, Rice | publisher = University of Michigan Press | year = 2007 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=F0dCiDh4fMsC | access-date = 2008-10-20 | isbn = 978-0-472-11627-0 | archive-date = 2021-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204092411/https://books.google.com/books?id=F0dCiDh4fMsC | dead-url = no }}</ref>在[[伊朗人质危机|伊朗人质危机]]和国内以高失业率和通货膨胀为标志且不断恶化的经济的帮助下，里根以压倒性的优势赢得了选举。<ref name="oldest">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1980/11/05/politics/05REAG.html|author=Hedrick Smith|title=Reagan Easily Beats Carter; Republicans Gain in Congress|newspaper=The New York Times|date=1980-11-05|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2017-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225034621/http://www.nytimes.com/1980/11/05/politics/05REAG.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Harold Jackson |author2=Alex Brummer |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/1980/nov/05/usa.alexbrummer |title=A landslide makes it President Reagan | US news |newspaper=The Guardians |date=1980-11-05 |access-date=2016-06-29 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129031521/https://www.theguardian.com/world/1980/nov/05/usa.alexbrummer |dead-url=no }}</ref>1980年的总统大选标志着里根时代的开始，也标志着美国政治保守派的[[政党重组|政党重组]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Troy |first=Gil |url=http://www.gilderlehrman.org/history-by-era/essays/age-reagan |title=The Age of Reagan | The Gilder Lehrman Institute of American History |website=Gilderlehrman.org |access-date=2016-06-29 |archive-date=2017-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171110044611/https://www.gilderlehrman.org/history-by-era/essays/age-reagan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Page |first=Susan |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/washington/2004-06-05-reagan-political-landscape_x.htm |title=USATODAY.com - Reagan's political force realigned political landscape |website=Usatoday30.usatoday.com |date=2004-06-06 |access-date=2016-06-29 |archive-date=2014-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141123072144/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/washington/2004-06-05-reagan-political-landscape_x.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2017年70岁的川普总统宣誓就职之前，69岁的里根是美国历史上就任时最年长的总统。<ref name="oldest"/>
